Common abbreviations:

   show      
   show_all
   on        --- attach signal handlers
   when      --- attach event handlers

Gagdet Makers:

   $.window       --- top level window
   $.b         --- labeled button
   $.l         --- label
   $.hbox      --- hbox
   $.vbox      --- vbox
   $.m         --- menu
   $.mi        --- menuitem
   $.menu_bar  --- menubar
   $.menu_item --- add menu item
   $.submenu   --- add submenu
   $.img       --- image
   ...

Signals:

   on.destroy 
   on.clicked 
   ...

Events:
   when.expose      
   when.button_press 
   ...

Attributes setting:

   set.title 
   set.text 
   ...
